Q2_What is org GOOD AT: Helping the people who live in their properties and the community with all different kind of services and resources. Such as finance classes, how to build and repair your credit, home ownership, how to budget, file your taxes, they also help with funding for individuals to attend an accredited school, college or program. They help assist with free child car seats, free pack n play playpens for baby's. They also help in many different ways as far as their residents needs when it comes to housing, helping pay bills and many other resources to help assist their residents and the community. I am very happy that I got the chance to find out about Homeport and the many great services that they provide! I am a Homeport resident and I am very thankful and appreciate everything that Homeport has been able to help and provide for me and my children. The staff and workers at Homeport are very nice, kind, friendly and helpful! I would like to thank Homeport for all of the help and resources that they have assisted me with! I received an email from Homeport and I am GLAD to take this survey. THANK YOU!
Q3_What could org DO BETTER: To be honest my opinion is nothing at this time. They work with you in a timely manner. They don't always answer when you call, but once you leave them a message they will give you a call back at their earliest convenience. They also let you know if they are going to be out of their office for a while or a certain period of time. But they will certainly return your call.
